  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: White </p><p></p><p>You can use your chakra threads to move your chakra to another space.</p><p> While you are connected to another creature via chakra threads, when you cast a Ninjutsu or Genjutsu, you can do so as though you were in that creature's space, but you must use your own senses.</p><p> This upgrade cannot be used with jutsu that have a range of Self.</p><p> Also, while connected to a creature you are aware of any jutsu based effects or conditions affecting them, if the creature acquires them while you are connected</p>",
